  [ Bryce Harrington ]
  * debian/patches/05_intel_exa_force_greedy.patch: Another shot at the
    greedy patch.  This time by slightly modifying the working patch by
    moving its logic outside the i965 if loop, so it'll apply to all
    hardware.  (LP: #177492)

  [ Timo Aaltonen ]
